text: This obsoletes IRM 4.87.1, Indian Tribal Governments, Inventory Management.

The material previously contained in IRM 4.87.1 pertaining to Inventory Management is incorporated into revised IRM 4.88.1, Indian Tribal Governments Examination Issues and Procedures, Examination Issues Pertaining to ITG Cases.
IRM 4.87.1, Indian Tribal Governments Inventory Management, is obsolete.
